@zxt5 Can you please fully reduce your submissions? You have correctly identified the optimization, but your alive proof includes unrelated instructions. All that is needed is this:
```llvm
define float @src(float %arg1) {
  %v2 = fadd float %arg1, 0.000000e+00
  %v3 = call float @llvm.fabs.f32(float %v2)
  ret float %v3
}

define float @tgt(float %arg1) {
  %v2 = call float @llvm.fabs.f32(float %arg1)
  ret float %v2
}
```
